divs: Sighting Detailshouse and dog sitting i took dogs out to bathroom it had just stopped raining saw a small yellowish white light with 2 red lights and a greenish blue one that spun somehow saw it wasnt really moving up or down but yellowish light was getting bigger and brighter red and blue light went off called mom told her what i saw she wanted me to go back in house then i could see it was coming closer it was moving told her i would call back it was over the middle school van buren the yellowish light got real bright and could see it lighting up near by clouds red lights came back on on the sides and blue light on was spinning some how it made no noise until it was right over the house it didnt sound like a plane or jet it was a quiet hum but at time sounded like acceleration i could see it was a metal looking objects diamond shape about house size speed slow enuff i could follow if i was on a bike i tried to take pix of it with the cam phone and they would not come out it then disappeared over the next two houses and i spoke to my mom again aand hen i could no longer see it or hear it i was shaking due to nerves and excitement i couldnt believe it dunno if it was gov or ufo but def nothing ive seen or heard of before someone else had to see it
